data.description: Come out and take a look at this ranch style constructed home just off HWY 47 near Chase City VA. The home has 2,208 Sq. Ft. of living space with 3 BDRM and 2.5 BR.  The home was originally built in 1990, the roof was replaced in/around 2000, and the windows were replaced in 2018. The home has a very large living room, 2 BDRM and 2 full BR downstairs, while the large primary suite and half bath is upstairs. The home has carpet throughout and a galley style kitchen just off the side entrance. The above ground pool conveys and has all of the pump/filter systems. The sellers are offering a one-year home warranty and up to $5000 in seller paid concessions or closing costs. The lot is approximately .64 acres and is zoned Agricultural. The home is located just outside the town of Chase City and North of Clarksville. This allows for easy access to services and amenities.
